[[tabview]]
[[tab 第一个世界]]
回忆：SCP-XXXX-1描绘了一个它不自觉间可以操控现实与时间的世界。它同时声称，许久以前曾有一段时间，这一它所拥有的世界乃是一切法则的中心，该法则以一切可被想象的方式统御所在宇宙。已无法获知在第一个SCP项目之前有何物存在过，亦无法知晓之后将存在什么；除开SCP-XXXX之外，当前的基金会已对此一无所知。

~ 由//Talk to Transformer//生成的文本
[[/tab]]

[[tab 第二个世界]]
SCP-XXXX描述了一个与他所出生的世界所相似的世界，但他使用了现在时。他提到一个名为Dr. O██████的个体需要为五名人类的死亡负责。此人建立了一座设施，通过受害者的身体制造人工灵魂。这座最终未能建成的设施可以每杀死一个人而制造数十个人类灵魂。他同时确认了数个SCP-XXXX个体。他描述称，他是在一场仪式中被杀死的，该仪式可以使他进入一个自己无法被发觉的平行维度之中，而且他在这一过程中创建的灵魂成为了死去个体的新身体。

~ 由//Talk to Transformer//生成的文本
[[/tab]]

[[tab 第三个世界]]
啊，那些来自大公司的人。那些试图通过科技统治世界的人。其中一人甚至与我的哥哥达成协议。他带我一起去，想让我在实验室里走向未来。我们在许多场合反反复复地谈论此事，但从未做出过任何成果。

~ 由//Talk to Transformer//生成的文本
[[/tab]]
[[/tabview]]

[[code type="css"]]

@import url(https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/scp-cn-tech/sigma9@cn/cn/sigma9_ch_wl.min.css);

/*
BASED ON FLANNEL NATURE CSS THEME
BASED ON SCP SIGMA-9 CSS THEME

Made by [[*user W Asriel]] for the Traveller's Book
*/


body{
    color: #222;
}

#container {    
    margin:0 5em 0 5em;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    -webkit-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    -moz-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    -o-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
}

div#container-wrap {
    background: url(https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/wanderers:travellers-book-hub/bg_C.jpg) repeat;
}

#page-title {
    color: #4b724b;
    border-bottom: 1px dotted #AAA;
}

#page-title:before {
    height:2em;
    width:2em;
    content:"　";
    background:url(https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/wanderers:travellers-book-hub/title_1.png) no-repeat 0px 0px;
    background-size: auto 1.1em;
}

#page-title:after {
    height:2em;
    width:2em;
    content:"　";
    background:url(https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/wanderers:travellers-book-hub/title_2.png) no-repeat 0px 0px;
    background-size: auto 1.1em;
}

h1,h2,h3 {
    color: #228B22;
}

blockquote{
    border: 1px dashed #008800;
    padding:0 3em 0 3em;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    -webkit-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2) !important;
    -moz-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2) !important;
    -o-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2) !important;

    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.code{
    border: 1px dashed #008800;
    padding:0 3em 0 3em;
    background:    rgba(236,242,226,0.8);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

a{
    color: #044004;    
    transition: background 0.5s ease-out;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-bottom:1px dashed #228B22;
}

a:hover{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
}

a.newpage{
    color: #888;
    transition: box-shadow 0.5s ease-out;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-bottom:1px dashed #228B22;
}

#side-bar {
    border: 1px solid #006600 !important;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    -webkit-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    -moz-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    -o-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
}

#side-bar a{
    border-bottom: none;
}

#side-bar .side-block {
    border: none;
    box-shadow: none;
    background:transparent !important;
}

#page-info{
    color: #555;
}

.page-options-bottom a{
    color: #242;
    background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom:none;
    transition: box-shadow 0.5s ease-out;
}
.page-options-bottom a:hover{
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

#header {
    font-family:'宋体' !important;
    width:100% !important;
    background:transparent !important;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #044004;
}

#header-extra-div-2{
    width:162px;
    height:162px;
    z-index: 0;
    background: transparent url(https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/wanderers:travellers-book-hub/tree.png);
    background-repeat:no-repeat;
    background-size:162px 162px;
    padding:0;
    margin:0;
    position: absolute;
    top:0; left:calc(25% - 9em);
}

#header h1{
    text-shadow:none !important;
    border-bottom:none;
}

#header h1 a {
    text-shadow:none !important;
    border-bottom:none;
}

#header h1 a::before {
//    color: #044004 !important;   
    color:transparent;
    font-family:'等线' !important;
    content: "旅行者之书";
    text-shadow:none !important;
}

#header h2{
    text-shadow:none !important;
    border-bottom:none;
}

#header h2 span {
    border-bottom:none;
    text-shadow:none !important;
}

#header h2 span::before {
    color:transparent;
    text-shadow:none !important;
}

#top-bar a {
    color: #044004;
    border-bottom:none;
    background: transparent;
}

#login-status {
    color: #333333;
}
#login-status a {
    color: #044004;
}

/* IMAGE BLOCK */
.image-block {
      margin:0 4%;
      border:2px solid #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 6px 20px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19);
    width: 300px;
}

.image-block.block-right {
    float: right;
    clear: right;
    margin: 0 2em 1em 2em;
}

.image-block.block-left {
    float: left;
    clear: left;
    margin: 0 2em 1em 0;
}

.image-block.block-center {
    margin-right: auto;
    margin-left: auto;
}
.image-block img {
    border: 0;
    width: 300px;
}
.image-block .image-caption {
    border-width:2px 0 0 0;
    border-style:solid;
    border-color:#fff;
    padding: 2px 0;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    -webkit-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    -moz-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    -o-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);

    font-size: 80%;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align: center;
    width: 300px;
}
.image-block > p {
    margin: 0;
}
.image-block .image-caption > p {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0 10px;
}

/* YUI TABS */
.yui-navset .yui-content{
    background-color:transparent;
    background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    -webkit-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1) !important;
    -moz-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1) !important;
    -o-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1) !important;

    padding-left: 2em;
    padding-right: 2em;
}
.yui-navset .yui-nav a,
.yui-navset .yui-navset-top .yui-nav a {
    background-color: #CCCCCC;
}
.yui-navset .yui-nav .selected a,
.yui-navset .yui-nav .selected a:focus,
.yui-navset .yui-nav .selected a:hover {
    background: #4b724b;
    color: #EEEEEE;
}
.yui-navset .yui-nav a:hover,
.yui-navset .yui-nav a:focus {
    background: #B4EEB4;
    text-decoration: none;
}
.yui-navset .yui-nav,
.yui-navset .yui-navset-top .yui-nav {
    border-color: #4b724b;
}
.yui-navset li {
    line-height: normal;
}

/* MOBILE ADJUSTMENTS */

@media (max-width: 767px) {
#container {    
    margin:0 0.5em 0 0.5em !important;
}

#side-bar{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5) !important;
    -webkit-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5) !important;
    -moz-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5) !important;
    -o-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5) !important;
}

#side-bar .close-menu {
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5) !important;
    -webkit-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5) !important;
    -moz-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5) !important;
    -o-background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5) !important;
}

}

[[/code]]
[[/iftags]]
